    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/926ed11530b2a07e50d71fff264df324.poster.avif?t=1687081647\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/926ed11530b2a07e50d71fff264df324.webm?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/926ed11530b2a07e50d71fff264df324.mp4?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Team Five 是回合制在线对战游戏，时间总是在和你作对！<br>指挥一支由五只拥有特殊能力的动物组成的小队，与好友一决高下。<br>尽力收集所有战利品，但不要太贪心哦！五分钟结束，世界就会毁灭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/fcfafb08075a8b58bd91b700f3c41856.poster.avif?t=1687081647\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/fcfafb08075a8b58bd91b700f3c41856.webm?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/fcfafb08075a8b58bd91b700f3c41856.mp4?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>尽情使用定制武器，火力全开！<br>打造属于自己的毁灭武器库，让武器改造升级，发挥最强功效。<br>倾泻怒火，燃烧一切摧毁万物，，甚至包括你自己！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/59ce5509bcd67c91d6060b74a1447fee.poster.avif?t=1687081647\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/59ce5509bcd67c91d6060b74a1447fee.webm?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/59ce5509bcd67c91d6060b74a1447fee.mp4?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>带回战利品后，你可以与神秘商贩交易，就是那只经历种种磨难的动物。<br>作为回报，他愿意用手中的宝物交换你收集到的战利品。<br>拥有强力武器、收集嗜血动物与酷炫的道具，为下一次冒险之旅保驾护航。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/aa656276a86012df5e2a61d132297ee3.poster.avif?t=1687081647\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/aa656276a86012df5e2a61d132297ee3.webm?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284160/extras/aa656276a86012df5e2a61d132297ee3.mp4?t=1687081647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 五只动物：指挥你的动物四处征战，利用它们的特殊技能和玩法创下战果。<br></li><li> 五个出口：收集所有散落的战利品，与对手一较高下，决定哪些动物可以在战斗中生存。<br></li><li> 五分钟：在限时战斗中享受酣畅淋漓的快感，谨慎做出决定，切忌犹豫不决。<br></li><li> 激烈的多人在线对战：挑战好友或与全球玩家一决雌雄。<br></li><li> 爆炸武器：定制并升级手中的武器，让巨大的威力震慑对手与环境。<br></li><li> 动态地图：破坏地型，倾泻怒火的同时改变地图的样貌。<br></li><li> 无限策略：尝试不同动物组合与策略方法，探索无穷无尽的战术潜能。</li></ul>",
